trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: FormCollection is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application> object to list the currently open forms in an application through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.OpenForms%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: FormCollection é utilizado pelo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application>objeto para listar os formulários atualmente abertos de uma aplicação através do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.OpenForms%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.OpenForms%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application>

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FormCollection"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an element in the collection by its numeric index.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um elemento na coleção pelo respetivo índice numérico.

trans-unit.source: The location of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"></xref> within the collection.
